{"tid":2104594,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"梁卓偉指港病毒變種後可「一傳四」 批檢測停滯 拒回應閻麗夢爆料","createTime":"2020-07-12T05:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T07:09:09.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"023a8384468353e565aaf33e3d160bf45b8d7594","tid":2104594,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200712/G23DPQ6FWFGSKPAFTQUC53CGAQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2FG23DPQ6FWFGSKPAFTQUC53CGAQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=98e468fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2FG23DPQ6FWFGSKPAFTQUC53CGAQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=d79368b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200712/G23DPQ6FWFGSKPAFTQUC53CGAQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n一變四，四變十二，來到這禮拜更加諷刺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉今日在節目中公佈最新疫情數據。他指，現時武漢肺炎病毒即時繁殖率接近「4」，即平均每一名武漢肺炎患者能夠傳染近4人。他解釋，由1月底約2.5至3的即時傳播率上升至今天接近4，原因在於病毒出現變種，而新品種的病毒614G的傳染能力相比舊有的614D上升31%。"},{"pid":"39575ee08d0f8459f470d52b8651d5b42b5945f7","tid":2104594,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"被問到曾在港大公共衛生學院工作的內地病毒學家閻麗夢，爆料指中國早知疫情會人傳人，但施壓令內地醫生噤聲，港大公共衞生學院教授潘烈文更着她「保持沉默並當心」，並警告她「不要觸碰紅線」，否則他們會有麻煩及有「被消失」的風險。梁指不認識閻，而港大昨晚已發聲明交代事件，不會再作回應，他個人亦沒有補充。梁又指，如細心看港大聲明，相信會理解更多事件的背景。"},{"pid":"489db133d19bd4839ff2250609df277fccf3848e","tid":2104594,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"講錯嘢一係名譽掃地一係俾中共夾上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老閪都封口啦"}]}